name: "A Estrela que se mexia"
description: A Estrela que se mexia - The Star that moved itself Lots of stars in the sky, in that wonderful new moon autumn night in Mata Atlântica forest. Muitas brilhavam, mas só ela se mexia. All of them shined, but only She was moving. Ela se mexeu demais, pra que eu não tivesse dúvidas. She moved a lot, for me to have no doubt that it was she: The Star that moved itself. Que ela era A Estrela que se mexia.  vivência, pintura, animation by Ronnie "Funilaria Espacial" Mata Atlantica, 2020
